The '''''Encyclopedic Dictionary of Astronomy''''' ({{lang-uk|Астрономічний енциклопедичний словник}}) is an [[Ukraine|Ukrainian]] encyclopedia of [[astronomy]]. It was published in 2003 and has around 3000 entries.<ref>{{Encyclopedic Dictionary of Astronomy}}</ref>

